comments: Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in Mobley's (CLE) path and marginal contact occurs as they engage and disengage during the pick.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in Allen's (CLE) path and does not deliver contact when setting the pick.
Mobley (CLE) gets to ball height and blocks Butler's (MIA) driving shot attempt and incidental contact occurs as both players return to the floor, following the block.
Okoro (CLE) holds his arms out slightly and marginal contact occurs with Oladipo (MIA) during the pick.
Oladipo (MIA) rests his forearm on Garland's (CLE) side and the contact during the drive is marginal.
Oladipo (MIA) legally contests Garland's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Garland (CLE) moves alongside Oladipo's (MIA) path and marginal contact occurs at the end of the drive.
Oladipo (MIA) briefly loses control of the ball during his gather before legally regathering the ball.
Garland (CLE) deflects Oladipo's (MIA) pass and incidental contact occurs with Butler (MIA) after the deflection.
Mobley (CLE) legally contests Oladipo's (MIA) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Okoro (CLE) establishes himself in Oladipo's (MIA) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the pick.
Adebayo (MIA) jumps and absorbs the marginal contact with Okoro (CLE) during his upward shooting motion near the rim.
Butler (MIA) initially establishes himself in Garland's (CLE) path and proceeds to reestablish himself as Garland shuffles towards the basket. The contact on the play is marginal.
Mobley (CLE) legally contests Adebayo's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Mitchell (CLE) extends his forearm into Martin's (MIA) side and the contact affects Martin's ability to pursue the loose ball.
Butler (MIA) moves alongside Mitchell's (CLE) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive into the frontcourt.
Adebayo (MIA) brings his hand to the ball and dislodges it during Mitchell's (CLE) dribble and Mitchell is able to immediately recover the ball.
Butler (MIA) brings his hand toward the ball and marginal arm contact occurs with Garland (CLE) as he releases his pass.
Butler (MIA) commits a take foul on Mitchell (CLE).
Rubio (CLE) does not inbound the ball within five seconds of receiving it from the official.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in Stevens' (CLE) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the screen.
Adebayo (MIA) firms up on his right leg and marginal contact occurs with Okoro (CLE) as he goes over the screen.
Okoro (CLE) legally contests Herro's (MIA) perimeter shot attempt.
Oladipo (MIA) is trailing Garland (CLE), who slips and goes to the ground on his own accord.
Adebayo (MIA) wraps his left arm around Allen's (CLE) waist and initiates contact that affects his ability to retrieve the pass.
Mobley (CLE) and Adebayo (MIA) both get to ball height and deflect the rebound. The arm contact after the deflection is considered incidental.
Butler (MIA) firms up in Mitchell's (CLE) path and absorbs the marginal body contact when setting the pick.
Mitchell (CLE) legally contests Strus' (MIA) perimeter shot attempt.
Okoro (CLE) momentarily brings his left arm across Adebayo's (MIA) back and marginal contact occurs during the rebounding opportunity.
Martin (MIA) commits a take foul on Mobley (CLE).
